dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.service.spec.rfs.ResourceFacingServiceSpecAtomic
dataStructure.description:
This is an abstract base class for defining ResourceFacingServiceSpecifications that do not have any subordinate ResourceFacingServiceSpecifications. In other words, a ResourceFacingServiceSpecAtomic is a stand-alone ResourceFacingServiceSpecification, and doesn't require any supporting ResourceFacingServiceSpecifications to define the invariant characteristics (i.e., non-changing attributes, methods, relationships, and constraints) of any ResourceFacingServices that it serves as a template for. Please see the DEN-ng Service Model whitepaper for more information and examples.

This entity is abstract

This entity is optional
dataStructure.label: ResourceFacingServiceSpecAtomic
